01:09:29,618 --> 01:09:32,519
That just doesn't look clear to me.
Another 30 minutes?

907
01:09:32,587 --> 01:09:34,521
- Yeah, maybe.
- The wing is...

908
01:09:34,589 --> 01:09:39,185
Whoa, whoa, wait a minute.
